				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">In case you have not noticed, the response to #5 of our top ten list has been changed. It was previously listed as being discussed.
<br />

<br />
Here is the request and the updated response:
<br />

<br />
 5) Streamline the item summoning process (more targeted summons) 
<br />

<br />
All summoned items should become targeted just like mod rods. 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">The current plan is to implement this change before Omens of War launches</span>
<br />

<br />
I will let you know of other responses as they become available<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://members.cox.net/dtresendes/danisig.png" border="0" />
<br />
