<br />

<br />
Pet heals need to be on-par with equivalent Beastlord heals HP-wise. The amount healed needs to be the same as beastlord heals, the cast time needs to be 3.75 seconds, and the recast time should be removed altogether. Higher level pet heals especially need a boost; in the time it takes to heal the pet, theres a high probability it is already dead. Also the amount currently healed is insufficient to equivalent level content (in Gates, for example, the 1200 HP healed from Planar Renewal is often less than one hit from random yard trash in Kod`Taz).
<br />

<br />
Currently being discussed (new details submitted)</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
